sql:
SELECT DISTINCT v.Vehicle_ID, v.Model
FROM vehicle v
LEFT JOIN vehicle_driver vd ON v.Vehicle_ID = vd.Vehicle_ID
GROUP BY v.Vehicle_ID, v.Model, v.Builder
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT vd.Driver_ID) >= 2 OR v.Builder = 'Ziyang'
question: What are the vehicle ids and models of the vehicle which have been driven by two drivers or been manufactured by 'Ziyang'.

sql:
SELECT Vehicle_ID, Model
FROM vehicle
WHERE Builder = 'Ziyang'
OR Vehicle_ID IN (
    SELECT Vehicle_ID
    FROM vehicle_driver
    GROUP BY Vehicle_ID
    HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT Driver_ID) >= 2
)
question: What are the vehicle ids and models of the vehicle which have been driven by two drivers or been manufactured by 'Ziyang'.

sql:
SELECT v.Vehicle_ID, v.Model
FROM vehicle v
LEFT JOIN vehicle_driver vd ON v.Vehicle_ID = vd.Vehicle_ID
LEFT JOIN driver d ON vd.Driver_ID = d.Driver_ID
GROUP BY v.Vehicle_ID, v.Model, v.Builder
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT vd.Driver_ID) = 2 OR v.Builder = 'Ziyang'
question: What are the vehicle ids and models of the vehicle which have been driven by two drivers or been manufactured by 'Ziyang'.

sql:
SELECT v.Vehicle_ID, v.Model
FROM vehicle v
LEFT JOIN vehicle_driver vd ON v.Vehicle_ID = vd.Vehicle_ID
LEFT JOIN driver d ON vd.Driver_ID = d.Driver_ID
GROUP BY v.Vehicle_ID, v.Model, v.Builder
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT vd.Driver_ID) = 2 OR v.Builder = 'Ziyang'
question: What are the vehicle ids and models of the vehicle which have been driven by two drivers or been manufactured by 'Ziyang'.

sql:
SELECT Vehicle_ID, Model FROM vehicle WHERE Builder = 'Ziyang'
UNION
SELECT vd.Vehicle_ID, v.Model
FROM vehicle_driver vd
JOIN vehicle v ON vd.Vehicle_ID = v.Vehicle_ID
GROUP BY vd.Vehicle_ID, v.Model
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT vd.Driver_ID) >= 2
